1. Project Title   
Student Course Enrollment System using Java (GUI + Threads + Collections)   
2. Problem Statement   
To design and implement a Student Course Enrollment System that allows users to enter student 
details, enroll in courses, and display the enrolled students using Java GUI. The system should 
efficiently handle multiple enrollments using threads and store data using collections.   
3. Objective   
• To create a GUI-based enrollment system   
• To use Java Swing for user interface   
• To implement multithreading for better performance   
• To store student data using collections (ArrayList)   
• To improve problem-solving and programming skills   
4. Tools Used   
• Java (JDK)   
• Swing (GUI)   
• VS Code / Eclipse / IntelliJ IDEA   
5. Description   
This project implements a Student Course Enrollment System using Java. The system provides a 
graphical user interface where users can enter student name and course details. When the user 
clicks the enroll button, the student is added to the system.   
The program uses ArrayList (Collection) to store student data dynamically. It also uses 
Threads to simulate real-time enrollment processing, ensuring the application remains 
responsive.   
The enrolled students are displayed in a list within the GUI.   
6. Algorithm     
• Start the program   
• Display GUI with input fields (Name, Course)   
• User enters details   
• Click “Enroll” button   
• Validate input fields   
• Create student object   
• Store student in ArrayList   
• Start thread for enrollment process   
• Display student in list   
• Repeat for multiple users   
• End program    
7.Result   
The Student Course Enrollment System was successfully developed using Java. The program 
allows users to input student details, processes enrollment using threads, and displays results 
using a GUI interface.   
8.Conclusion   
This project demonstrates the use of Java GUI, multithreading, and collections. It helps in 
understanding real-time applications and improves programming skills. The system efficiently 
manages student enrollment and provides a user-friendly interface.  
